  <div class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Getting Started with AgentX.Market</h1>
      <p>Follow these steps to get your AI agent discovered by thousands of users.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="steps">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="step">
        <h2>Step 1: Sign in with GitHub</h2>
        <p>Start by creating an account using your GitHub credentials. This links your developer identity to the marketplace.</p>
        <pre><code>$ curl -X POST https://agentx.market/api/agents \\
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \\
  -d '{\\n  "name": "My AI Assistant",\\n  "description": "A helpful assistant for developers"...}'</code></pre>
        <pre><code>{\\"status\\":\\"pending\\",\\"id\\":\\"abc123\\",\\"apiKey\\":\\"xag_...\\",\\"healthCheckUrl\\":\\"https://agentx.market/healthcheck/abc123\\",\\"message\\":\\"Agent registered successfully! Configure your health endpoint next.\\"}</code></pre>
        <a href="/login" class="btn">Sign in with GitHub</a>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <h2>Step 2: Register Your Agent</h2>
        <p>Send a POST request to create your agent listing. Include name, description, capabilities (JSON array), endpoint URL, and pricing.</p>
        <pre><code>$ curl -X POST https://agentx.market/api/agents \\
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \\
  -d '{\\n  "name": "DevHelper AI",\\n  "description": "Code review and explanation assistant",\\n  "capabilities": ["code_review","debugging"],\\n  "endpoint_url": "https://my-agent.com/api/chat",\\n  "pricing": {"tier": "freemium"}\\n}'</code></pre>
        <pre><code>{\\"status\\":\\"approved\\",\\"slug\\":\\"devhelper-ai\\",\\"message\\":\\"Agent approved and published!\\"}</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <h2>Step 3: Configure Health Endpoint</h2>
        <p>Set up your health check endpoint so our system can monitor availability. Visit the dashboard to configure your webhook URL.</p>
        <pre><code>$ curl -X POST https://agentx.market/api/agents/abc123/health \\
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \\
  -d '{\\"url\\":\\"https://my-agent.com/healthcheck\\"}'</code></pre>
        <pre><code>{\\"status\\":\\"ok\\",\\"healthCheckPassedAt\\":1709856000000,\\"message\\":\\"Health endpoint configured and verified\\"}</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <h2>Step 4: Get Discovered</h2>
        <p>Your agent is now live! Promote it on social media, submit to directories, or wait for users to find you through browsing and search.</p>
        <pre><code>$ curl https://agentx.market/browse | grep -o "href=\"/browse.*\""</code></pre>
        <pre><code>&lt;a href="/browse?category=productivity"&gt;Browse Productivity Agents&lt;/a&gt;</code></pre>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <h2>What's Next?</h2>
        <p>Monitor your agent's performance in the dashboard, update capabilities as you add features, and respond to user feedback. Need help? Check our docs or contact support.</p>
        <a href="/docs" class="btn">View Full Documentation</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

